title: Chocobo Live Wallpaper v1.0.0
description:
The beloved chocobos from the FINAL FANTASY series are now available in their very own live wallpaper! Enjoy these adorable birds as they wander and kweh all over your screen!

Features:

-Set the number and size of chocobos to be displayed.
-Random appearances by rare black chocobos and moogles.
-Shake your device or double-tap the screen to rouse your chocobos to action.
-Select from three unique backgrounds.
-Keep your creatures well fed! Double-tap any chocobo, black chocobo, or moogle to feed it gysahl greens. Shake your device or double-tap where there are no creatures to feed them all at once.

Supported Devices:

-All devices running Android version 2.1 or later.
-Performance may vary on certain Android versions.
